    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个架构图，展示用户如何通过Claude UI与SolidWorks进行交互。核心场景是用户既直接操作SolidWorks，又通过自然语言让AI辅助设计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "👤 user",
        "☁️ claude ui",
        "🔧 solidworks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那MCP Host在这里是什么角色？是Claude和SolidWorks之间的桥梁吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "🧠 mcp host"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，MCP Host是中间层。用户从Claude UI发送指令，MCP Host负责处理这些请求，然后转换成SolidWorks能理解的API调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "🧠 mcp host",
        "☁️ claude ui"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出三个核心节点：用户、Claude UI、SolidWorks，再加上MCP Host作为中间枢纽。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "👤 user",
        "☁️ claude ui",
        "🧠 mcp host",
        "🔧 solidworks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "MCP Host内部需要细分一下。它有个Context Builder模块，负责把用户的自然语言指令结合当前SolidWorks的上下文，生成结构化的Prompt Template。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "🧠 mcp host",
        "conte",
        "prompttemplate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Context Builder的数据来源是什么？它需要知道SolidWorks当前的选中状态、模型结构这些信息吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "conte",
        "modeldata",
        "acti"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。我们需要两个数据流：一个是Event Capture监听SolidWorks的实时事件和选中变化，进入Action Queue；另一个是Model Data直接读取模型的特征、尺寸等静态结构。两者都汇聚到Context Builder。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "eventcapture",
        "acti",
        "modeldata",
        "conte"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我画出了Event Capture和Model Data两个节点，都指向Context Builder。Action Queue作为中间缓冲，处理焦点元素和历史记录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "eventcapture",
        "acti",
        "modeldata",
        "conte"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Prompt Template生成后，其实还要回到MCP Host做最终处理。另外，我们需要一个Version Manager来处理不同SolidWorks版本的兼容性问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "prompttemplate",
        "🧠 mcp host"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Version Manager是放在Python Layer里，还是独立一层？考虑到它要管理多个版本的API文档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pyth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "放在Python Layer里，和Context Builder、Prompt Template一起。然后Version Manager下面挂一个Adapter层，专门处理版本适配。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "pyth",
        "adapterlayer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
